annotations.description: Not only is it officially fall but October is National Applejack Month and we decided to celebrate with five distinctive cocktails to help you ring in the Ho...
annotations.title: Celebrating National Applejack Month with 5 Cocktails!

textContent:
2oz (60ml) Applejack
.75oz (22.5ml) Lemon
.75oz (22.5ml) Orgeat
2 Dashes Angostura Bitters
Mint Sprig Garnish

Light shake just to chill. 
Pour into rocks glass
Top with crushed ice
